{"tid":875744,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國偶像瘋game！OGN將播出綜藝電競大賽","createTime":"2018-10-25T05:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T12:38:27.000Z","uid":1086,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3e1166babb15e97600c21fe99251765db3cc33fe","tid":875744,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T05:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/158/5bd0518388bfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F158%2F5bd0518388bfa.jpg&h=ded9a840&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有許多韓國偶像都相當熱愛遊戲。照片為知名韓團Super Junior的成員希澈與神童cosplay成《英雄聯盟》角色李星與阿璃。   圖：翻攝自 smtown 粉絲專頁</span><br />\n<br />\n韓國偶像也瘋電競！CJ ENM遊戲頻道「OGN」近日表示將會結合偶像與遊戲的元素，舉行類似於偶像運動會的「Gamedolympic」，消息一出引發粉絲熱烈討論，紛紛猜測究竟哪幾位偶像會登場！<br />\n<br />\nCJ ENM遊戲頻道「OGN」將舉行號稱韓國國內最大演藝界電競大會「Gamedolympic」，這個節目將邀請愛好遊戲的偶像與藝人，並進行熱門遊戲項目如<span style=\"color: red;\">《英雄聯盟》、《絕地求生》、《Battle Stars VR》</span>等項目，屆時會把參賽者分作4組進行各項目的淘汰賽，每個項目都有不同的賽制，《英雄聯盟》會進行四強淘汰賽，《絕地求生》將大戰五回合選出吃雞冠軍，《Battle Stars VR》也會以淘汰賽的方式進行，也會準備較為簡易的遊戲來進行簡單的競賽。<br />\n<br />\n消息一出引發粉絲熱烈討論，紛紛推薦自家偶像登場，其中呼聲最高的莫過於加盟TEAM KONGDOO的知名歌手兼職業選手鄭俊英、Super Junior<span style=\"color: red;\">希澈</span>、EXO的<span style=\"color: red;\">Baekhyun</span>、GOT7的<span style=\"color: red;\">Mark</span>、TWICE的<span style=\"color: red;\">Mina</span>、Day6的 <span style=\"color: red;\">Jae</span>等人，更有人大推由B.A.P的永才號召組成的團隊「我們是最強愛豆」，成員包含BTOB<span style=\"color: red;\">恩光</span>、VIXX的<span style=\"color: red;\">Ken</span>、BTS <span style=\"color: red;\">Jin</span>、Wanna One的<span style=\"color: red;\">朴志訓</span>等人，如果這幾位偶像聚在一起肯定會擦出特別不一樣的火花。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/158/5bd05894adb7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F158%2F5bd05894adb7f.jpg&h=9f178696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">偶像參與遊戲電競相關的節目也不是頭一遭了，先前Super Junior希澈便曾參加過SBS 節目《Game Show 遊戲樂樂》（圖：翻攝自 나무위키）</span><br />\n<br />\n而偶像參與遊戲電競相關的節目也不是頭一遭了，先前Super Junior希澈便曾參加過SBS 打造的遊戲相關綜藝節目《Game Show 遊戲樂樂》（게임쇼 유희낙락），他在節目中大談遊戲經，更表示自己在競爭激烈的《英雄聯盟》韓國伺服器中擁有鑽石排位，而他也希望能夠藉此破除社會對於「玩遊戲等於不務正業」的偏見，推廣健康的遊戲文化。這檔「Gamedolympic」節目預計會在11月中旬透過OGN頻道播出，屆時究竟誰會上場，粉絲都相當期待。"},{"pid":"896c5b1426c2e4f4fc973b1784785d8565f0441d","tid":875744,"uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:09:02.000Z","msg":"撐MINA"},{"pid":"2e891721eb3312db18064c99772906f1511643ac","tid":875744,"uid":80814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"偶運會收皮, 就到玩電莖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af86045b5ccfd8958b26caceb987d6e18d3e79f7","tid":875744,"uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:17:44.000Z","msg":"電莖就係電莖<br />\n請k pop star唔會變高檔啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db85a0611a817f0fee0674ac31c90d7b5d48f9aa","tid":875744,"uid":1408,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e891721eb3312db18064c99772906f1511643ac","tid":875744,"uid":80814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"偶運會收皮, 就到玩電莖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:18:09.000Z","msg":"坐係室內打機點都好過出去跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37153f712446abba804eb301d0d990431e67d0ed","tid":875744,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db85a0611a817f0fee0674ac31c90d7b5d48f9aa","tid":875744,"uid":1408,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e891721eb3312db18064c99772906f1511643ac","tid":875744,"uid":80814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"